palette_data.reasoning: This palette combines soft pastels with vibrant accents to evoke a whimsical, light-hearted mood. The pastel pink (#FFD1DC) and mint green (#9FE2BF) provide a gentle, dreamy base, while the bright coral (#FFB347) and turquoise (#40E0D0) add energetic pops of color. The periwinkle (#836FFF) brings balance with a cool tone, harmonizing the warmth and freshness to create visual delight.
